title: Ep.7: Chiefs Playoff Chances, Lakers Struggles, Packers vs Cardinals Preview, and More
description: The sports world is buzzing as the NFL and NBAs top teams (Chiefs and Lakers) are off to rocky starts. Can they turn it around and contend for a championship? Can Green Bay end the cardinals 7-0 win streak without their top players? Tune in to this episode to find out more!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
